programme.desc: 酒樓負責人疑因找續問題與顧客發生口角，繼而遭襲擊，當事人親述受傷經過。某戶主稱回鄉後返港，驚見深水埗住所被老鼠入侵並四處破壞，懷疑跟樓宇大維修有關。老翁大便出血，曾到兩間公立醫院診治均未能查出病因，醫生亦沒有安排照腸鏡，老翁最終因大腸癌離世。八旬妻子控訴醫院專業失當，醫委會調查後卻判定投訴不成立？郭子豪、鄧卓殷宣佈訂婚，並透過錄音分享喜悅。孔德賢於情人節在街頭派花，順道宣傳熱播劇《本尊就位》。

programme.desc: 禮榮、寶生及滿基到海灘燒烤作樂，彼此談及感情事。禮榮稱與前女友郭希雯分手後便沒有再拍拖。希雯是泳珊的女兒，寶生直認至今仍對她念念不忘。希雯突然出現，表示因自己的公關公司負責長洲母校重建計畫，所以重回此地。寶生問禮榮會否重新追求希雯，否則自己會展開追求，這時寶生看見醉醺醺的朱鈴鈴走來，不禁叫慘。希雯邀母親遷往市區同住，泳珊卻擔心希雯與男友的關係。禮榮與希雯在街上遇到妙蓮，妙蓮邀希雯到家飲湯。希雯欲在禮榮房間找出他女友的照片，卻見書枱上仍放著當年她送給禮榮的水晶蘋果。

programme.desc: 秦姨娘有意讓琥珀看到佟姨娘的半條手帕，並稱佟姨娘的死與元娘有關；徐太夫人準備給令宜納妾，琥珀有意向杜媽媽說起令宜貼身衣物丟失，而杜媽媽向太夫人提起此事，認為是冬青拿的，於是太夫人想到給令宜納冬青為妾。

programme.title: 愛．回家之開心速遞#2209[粵]
programme.desc: 農曆新年前，樹根見家人喜歡吃他烹調的年糕與蘿蔔糕，遂購入大量材料炮製更多糕點。熊家眾人過年時吃下極多糕，已到了「聞糕色變」的地步，怎料那些賀年糕點竟然「陸續有來」。樹仁想到將那些糕「送走」的方法，卻事與願違……熊家眾人似乎對年糕、蘿蔔糕患上恐懼症，樹根仍設法逼大家吃糕，眾人痛苦不已，此時卻發現樹根有所隱瞞，尚善打算要讓樹根得到應有的教訓……

programme.title: 本尊就位#15[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 士豪將在西郊空地興建煙館及賭坊，正義遊說村民反對方案。不過，村民其後被士豪賄賂，並以民意逼迫正義批准更改土地用途，木昆現身成功扭轉民意。大剛向士豪透露木昆的神棍身份，與士豪開始盤算復仇大計。木昆起程尋找曉飛口中的花瓶，沒發現寶藏，卻拾獲一支玉簪。木昆得到玉簪似得到了神力保護，成功擋下手槍射出的子彈，隨後在公眾場合為鎮民施法醫病，贏得全鎮掌聲。士豪見識木昆法力，只好向正義求和，但二人不歡而散。

programme.title: 狀王之王#14[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 世傑再與浩信一夥見面，稱已為對方安排跟正堂交易。阿九假扮正堂現身，與浩信約定交易地點；有人向正堂報信揭露世傑身分。小鳳帶人營救遭壓榨的礦工；世傑、阿九與浩信交易，其間玲瓏被揭穿假扮護衛……世傑全家來到京城，原來有神秘人禮聘世傑赴京；眾人在街道行逛，碰見有男子喊冤。世傑與神秘人會面，對方竟是京城第一狀師談蕭陽，他希望世傑接辦一宗英國使節的案件，世傑未有即時答應。世傑及後偶遇珊珊，還看到她被人非禮……

programme.title: 尋找世界另一個我 台灣篇[粵]
programme.desc: 以為不易撞名，原來台北亦有一位譚俊彥老師！譚老師帶Shaun來到他於十歲前居住的萬華區，細訴自己的童年生活。Shaun還得悉了一個驚愕真相，令他覺得「好痴線」？三個譚俊彥臨時組織車隊，在卡丁車賽場來一場友誼賽，結果當然是三甲席位由譚俊彥稱霸！再到豪華露營場地，打開心窗無所不談，譚老師也笑說做過最壞的事情！雖然旅程只有三天，Shaun都為其餘兩位譚俊彥製作了紀念冊，並以結他自彈自唱送上驚喜。

programme.desc: 梁芷珮認為沒有到過荷里活大道，走過星光大道，看過荷里活電影舉行首映禮的戲院，不算遊過LA，所以她通通做齊！她又參加由私人導遊開辦的「荷里活狗仔隊團」，在車上遠眺名人巨星的家；之後遊覽著名音樂頒獎禮主題博物館，以及集吃、買、欣賞表演於一身的墨西哥街Olvera Street。玩得意猶未盡，她還去到La Jolla Cove沙灘，近距離看看海獅和海豹。

programme.desc: 新一輯繼續精彩絕倫，主持米高乘坐鐵路旅行，探索英倫群島的沿海地區，環遊英倫四個國家的海岸，重新遊覽英國沿海地區的區域特色，各地離岸都僅為 70 英里。米高將利用鐵路提供的獨特通道，體驗英國壯麗的風景山色。

programme.desc: 沿著巴塔哥尼亞的大西洋海岸之旅，那裡的土地可能貧瘠，但海洋卻充滿生機。在這個荒涼無情的地方，虎鯨冒著一切危險求生，而巨大的雄性象海豹則在爭奪繁殖的機會。而七萬多隻鸚鵡則在躲避地上最快的動物：游隼。

programme.title: 100道風味[英]
programme.desc: 身處智能小工具和科技時代，很難想像現代生活中，架上放著一堆積滿灰塵的食譜。 本節目令觀眾領略烹飪傑作的微妙之處，你會發現世上三百種遠近馳名的佳餚。從日本到美國，從德國到馬來西亞等等！

programme.title: 明珠930:冰河世紀2[英/粵]

programme.desc: 節目突破以色彩和軟裝為主的傳統裝修形式，聚焦於空間改變和功能實現上。由頂尖設計師以有限的資金，在有限的空間裡，根據委託人的特殊需求進行徹底改造。通過設計師的匠心巧思，完成看似不可能的家裝夢想。

programme.title: 沒玩過的台北[粵/普]
programme.desc: 傳統景點不再滿足勇於見識的旅遊達人，主持誓要發掘台北的秘點角落。復古文具店是隱藏窄巷的大驚喜，只售賣逾五十年的古董貨品，惟全部文具均屬新品，最古老的玻璃筆、五十年代古董複印機，簡直像時光倒流。三人到茶屋細嚐非一般香茶，茶瓶不同編號代表茶的發酵程度，再分四種沖茶方式，喝得高品質。發掘獨特的洗衣複合式咖啡店，邊等待洗衣邊品嚐甜點夠貼心。韻潔領軍吃海鮮鍋，有多款蝦選擇，「海鮮博士」即席傳授煮蝦技巧！

programme.title: 還原神之食[粵]
programme.desc: 劇集《東坡家事》內，萬綺雯為還原「蘇東坡」娘親的巧手味道，機緣巧合下創出了「東坡肉」。泳芍、欣茵拜訪「小鮮肉」廚藝高手，要求他嘗試還原「東坡肉」。劇中情節有交代萬綺雯曾蒸煮「東坡肉」，小鮮肉廚師亦指相關步驟可令瘦肉部位變得軟腍。試食時間，泳芍盡情張開嘴巴，把肥瘦相間的「東坡肉」一口放進嘴裡，臉上隨即洋溢幸福表情。積奇則帶來一道承傳自父親的特別版東坡肉，也是瑞士人的賀年菜，而且做法非常簡單！

programme.title: 以家人之名#1[粵/普]
programme.desc: 李尖尖自幼喪母，爸爸李海潮開了一間麵館，獨力養育女兒，李家樓上搬來凌和平一家，李尖尖一直想要一個哥哥，看到凌霄非常喜歡，賀梅離異，帶著七歲的兒子子秋，李尖尖不想賀梅當繼母，連帶子秋一起討厭。

programme.title: 2024開運救兵[粵]
programme.desc: 美棋BB(黃美棋)「好事近」，感情發展一向順利，仍祈求事業步步高陞！三位師傅怎樣幫她？九運大利北方，旺事業與生意的方位卻有不同？Depp為美棋BB看家居風水，擺放甚麼火元素的東西能趨吉避凶？裸泳為美棋BB打造「開運Look」，橙色、黃色的服飾「夠搶眼」，原來指甲、胭脂以至電話殼的顏色都「幫到手」！慧慧教授「開路魔法」，用土、水、火、風元素的代表物淨化鎖匙後，如何再為鎖匙「加持」達至「路路暢通」？

programme.title: 一條麻甩在廣州[粵]
programme.desc: 廣州，粵菜發源地之一，廣府菜的中心，是每一位食客都無法拒絕的美食聖地。愛吃愛玩的主持人麥包，在廣州徹底釋放了吃貨天性，走遍大街小巷，尋找地道美食：悠閑早茶、西關小吃、新潮佳饌，夜市小攤...

programme.title: 不正常愛情研究所[粵]
programme.desc: 甜蜜過情人節，禮物或大餐較重要？倩彤看重對方心意；國麟認為兩者都非重點，有愛就夠，獲永衡盲撐！男友慶祝情人節時發火走人，紫恩不捨任食貴價蟹竟留低喊住食……國麟自製大餐卻變食杯麵？敏芝則難忘與男友在宿舍煮飯仔共度首個情人節。假設另一半提議情人節食米線，永衡激讚要結婚，但女拍檔們好嫌棄！私房菜餐廳大廚Kenny認同男生識烹飪會加分，紫恩卻關心他下廚時可有著衫？嘉賓另會細談送兩束花，及煮數十人大餐經歷。

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#18[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 故事講述一名背叛了丈夫和生病的兒子，為了愛情和慾望拋家棄子的母親，與懷著對母親怨恨的女兒多年後再次見面，並開始對自己母親展開復仇計畫。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 港產魔術師甄澤權（Louis）憑高超「魔法」在外國人主導的魔術界，變出一片璀璨天地。身為華人魔術師，他如何自評優勢？Louis喜歡叫觀眾參與表演，對近距離魔術更別具心得。但如碰上不合作的現場朋友，他會如何應對？他還帶來一副啤牌即場表演，梓軒欣賞過後不禁高呼「點解嘅」！大家或有想學魔術的念頭，行內規則「不會無代價傳授魔術」是甚麼一回事？Louis又細說拍攝《街頭魔法王》點滴，提到當中魔術均是原創！

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 港產魔術師甄澤權（Louis）再次獻技，電線膠布在他手中亦可變出驚人「魔法」！阿范與梓軒的金晴火眼又能否看出當中端倪？Louis竟然破例「教」兩位主持把撕碎紙巾還原的魔術，二人原來已成為另一魔幻表演的構成部份……Louis又說起同業要保守魔法秘密的行規，但多年前曾出現一位蒙面魔術師高調揭秘，業界如何看待事件？他亦有意成立魔法學院，讓孩子有更多機會接觸魔術，更提到「入魔」可為小朋友帶來不少益處？

programme.title: 姊妹淘[粵]
programme.desc: 今集「姊妹心頭好」，嘉賓陳凱琳(Grace)、蔡思貝(Sisley)及主持們就帶來了她們覺得最難忘的聖誕禮物，當中尤以楊秀惠及Sisley的最為特別。楊秀惠帶來的是一隻手錶，那是她媽媽送給她的禮物，儘管已經不能再用，但她仍然保存至今。至於Sisley的禮物則是從外國的古董店帶回來，而且是古代公主所佩戴過，大家猜得到那是甚麼嗎？一朵小花或一片樹葉也可以做成藝術品，那就是押花藝術。押花藝術家Trista非常醉心於製作各種押花物品，今集Trista會教大家製作一只押花玻璃碟。

programme.title: 女醫神Doctor X 7#5[粵/日][PG]
programme.desc: 多年前曾與未知子一同做過一場手術的派遣護士那須田，因其高傲的態度及作為護士的本領令未知子留下深刻印象；恰巧被東帝臨時僱用的她，在第一次手術時已與執刀醫師興梠鬧出不快場面，被興梠勒令離開手術室…

programme.title: 野外步出[粵]
programme.desc: 奶仔相約識於微時的好友趙慧珊Aka，一同攀石運動中的「游繩下降」。攀石又稱「牆上芭蕾」，Aka芭蕾舞根底深厚，可有優勢？二人先來小試牛刀，在山野間初次試玩，Aka還應奶仔要求一邊下降一邊唱歌。不過，當登上山崗將城市美景盡收眼底後，他們卻開始為高度感到害怕。在挑戰雙人版的游繩下降時，奶仔竟要Aka懸於半空吃雞蛋，會是甚麼滋味？此外，Aka會分享當初由DJ「變身」跳唱組合成員的心情，並笑稱其實是打雜！

programme.title: 野外步出[粵]
programme.desc: 奶仔與嘉賓李旻芳是藝員訓練班的師兄妹，這次選擇划雙人獨木舟更與這出身有關？穿上救生衣準備啟程，但甫登艇已遇驚險。二人出海划到海中小島，並在沙灘上自煮韓式部隊鍋，奶仔還「潛來」龍蝦與墨魚加餸？兩位藝訓班畢業生有不少共同話題，旻芳透露當初上課已定下目標向主持領域發展。旻芳又「投訴」奶仔早前於網上節目未有邀請她任嘉賓！今集後記，旻芳稱讚奶仔拍攝認真，也對其主持表現感到滿意，但評分時卻只得六十分？

programme.title: 就是愛美麗[粵/普]
programme.desc: 好的胭脂會為面色加分，美妝達人高毓喬(Minnie)解說霜、粉、膏、液狀胭脂的特色，冷、暖色系膚色適合的胭脂顏色，以及不同臉型塗抹胭脂的技巧。「愛美麗時尚」參觀台北國際美妝展，展覽涵蓋美妝、美髮、美甲和各式保養，更有知名專家到場作分享，彩妝達人小凱老師就為大家推介木質調胭脂。「愛美麗盲測」測試四款開架發售的日本品牌胭脂，評比它們的易推度、妝感和防水度，讓大家選對產品，打造紅粉緋緋好面色。

programme.title: 就是愛美麗[粵/普]
programme.desc: 感冒時要吃維他命C，但原來平常保養也需要它！保養專家袁觀玲解說維他命C的六大功效，提醒大家使用維他命C保養品及口服維他命C產品的注意事項。「網絡紅什麼」教授DIY防過量進食美肌排毒水及瘦小腹排毒水，讓大家喝水喝出美麗。台北市西區最具指標性的購物區西門町，一直是遊客必去的重點行程，「愛美麗時尚」走訪區內一間天然植萃髮廊，客人可護理頭皮，體驗自然有機的玫瑰精露頭皮護理SPA。

programme.title: MUSIC BREAK[粵]
programme.desc: 本集由林沚羿(@venus.img)推介歌單，播放的MV包括《J Music》主持《越唱越強》、《亞洲超星團》《新年快樂2024》；「勁歌金榜No.1」薛家燕、茜拉Shila《有有有Year of the Yo!》；《中年好聲音2》十四強《中年好運來》、劉德華《恭喜發財‧大吉祥》；張學友、鄭秀文《恭喜你》；劉德華、軟硬天師、關淑怡、譚詠麟、李克勤、黃凱芹、黃翊、草蜢、張學友《恭喜恭喜》等。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 激勵演說家車志健對於待人處事自有一番見解，更曾上載一條「教人不介意做衰人」的短片，其實只是希望大家勇於表達自己的真實思想。志健相信「近朱者赤，近墨者黑」，並提到某些人士不宜結交，當中有何特徵？志健經常鼓勵人要突破、超越自我，而他從健身教練「變身」教導銷售技巧的導師，便是現成例子。志健認為人的潛能無限，只要肯花心思、時間，做任何事皆可成功。Bob就此提出對方做生意失敗的經歷，志健又怎樣回應？

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 見工是一門學問，要如何表現自己才可得到僱主垂青？嘉賓車志健以自我推銷比喻面試，還解釋穿著儀容與資料搜集對面試的重要性。志健提到一個不少見工者的常犯錯誤，就是自我介紹時複述履歷表上的工作經驗，怎樣才是恰當做法？Bob亦趁機分享可令老闆留下深刻印象的面試秘訣！僱主常會要求應徵人士細說自己的長處與短處，應該如何回答方能增加受聘機會？志健又建議求職者在公司與個人同步發展一環多作思考，這樣才可望突圍而出！

programme.title: 沒玩過的台北[粵/普]
programme.desc: 桃園機場捷運開通後，韻潔、書孟與子芸發掘林口區，來一日輕旅行！首站到地標Outlet狂買到破產！三人買鬆脆可口的黃金餅伴手禮醫肚；書孟牽頭感受書卷味，購平價新書至抵！三人到製茶廠，當一天小茶農，有口福品嚐地道冠軍林口茶。來到少女甜點下午茶聖地打卡，書孟要先說出通關密碼才可吃限定鹹點？三人「大戰」巨型龍蝦，書孟嚇得差點掉頭走！豪華海鮮塔逐層吃盡新鮮海產，還有最底層的海鮮精華粥，吸盡鮮味湯汁。

programme.title: 還原神之食[粵]
programme.desc: 「夫妻肺片」是古裝劇《金玉滿堂》的王牌菜，歐陽震華還藉此成為御廚。欣茵、泳芍向正宗川菜大廚朱先文拜師學藝，嘗試重現這道四川名菜。煮法、擺盤有學問，牛湯底與紅油更是靈魂所在！菜油煮滾後，為何要分三次倒入辣椒碎？見識過師傅刀功，泳芍也要挑戰切牛脷薄片，卻成厚切豪華版？瑞士都有「夫妻肺片」？積奇帶來「懷舊瑞士煮牛肚」，還教大家用西式方法去除內臟腥味。炒蔬菜碎要以慢火兜至焦香，欣茵欠耐性，唯有請積奇出手！

programme.title: 以家人之名#1[粵/普]
programme.desc: 李尖尖自幼喪母，爸爸李海潮開了一間麵館，獨力養育女兒，李家樓上搬來凌和平一家，李尖尖一直想要一個哥哥，看到凌霄非常喜歡，賀梅離異，帶著七歲的兒子子秋，李尖尖不想賀梅當繼母，連帶子秋一起討厭。

programme.title: 一條麻甩在廣州[粵]
programme.desc: 廣州，粵菜發源地之一，廣府菜的中心，是每一位食客都無法拒絕的美食聖地。愛吃愛玩的主持人麥包，在廣州徹底釋放了吃貨天性，走遍大街小巷，尋找地道美食：悠閑早茶、西關小吃、新潮佳饌，夜市小攤...

programme.title: 不正常愛情研究所[粵]
programme.desc: 甜蜜過情人節，禮物或大餐較重要？倩彤看重對方心意；國麟認為兩者都非重點，有愛就夠，獲永衡盲撐！男友慶祝情人節時發火走人，紫恩不捨任食貴價蟹竟留低喊住食……國麟自製大餐卻變食杯麵？敏芝則難忘與男友在宿舍煮飯仔共度首個情人節。假設另一半提議情人節食米線，永衡激讚要結婚，但女拍檔們好嫌棄！私房菜餐廳大廚Kenny認同男生識烹飪會加分，紫恩卻關心他下廚時可有著衫？嘉賓另會細談送兩束花，及煮數十人大餐經歷。

programme.title: 女醫神Doctor X 7#5[粵/日][PG]
programme.desc: 多年前曾與未知子一同做過一場手術的派遣護士那須田，因其高傲的態度及作為護士的本領令未知子留下深刻印象；恰巧被東帝臨時僱用的她，在第一次手術時已與執刀醫師興梠鬧出不快場面，被興梠勒令離開手術室…

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#18[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 故事講述一名背叛了丈夫和生病的兒子，為了愛情和慾望拋家棄子的母親，與懷著對母親怨恨的女兒多年後再次見面，並開始對自己母親展開復仇計畫。

programme.title: 2024開運救兵[粵]
programme.desc: 美棋BB(黃美棋)「好事近」，感情發展一向順利，仍祈求事業步步高陞！三位師傅怎樣幫她？九運大利北方，旺事業與生意的方位卻有不同？Depp為美棋BB看家居風水，擺放甚麼火元素的東西能趨吉避凶？裸泳為美棋BB打造「開運Look」，橙色、黃色的服飾「夠搶眼」，原來指甲、胭脂以至電話殼的顏色都「幫到手」！慧慧教授「開路魔法」，用土、水、火、風元素的代表物淨化鎖匙後，如何再為鎖匙「加持」達至「路路暢通」？

programme.title: 野外步出[粵]
programme.desc: 奶仔相約識於微時的好友趙慧珊Aka，一同攀石運動中的「游繩下降」。攀石又稱「牆上芭蕾」，Aka芭蕾舞根底深厚，可有優勢？二人先來小試牛刀，在山野間初次試玩，Aka還應奶仔要求一邊下降一邊唱歌。不過，當登上山崗將城市美景盡收眼底後，他們卻開始為高度感到害怕。在挑戰雙人版的游繩下降時，奶仔竟要Aka懸於半空吃雞蛋，會是甚麼滋味？此外，Aka會分享當初由DJ「變身」跳唱組合成員的心情，並笑稱其實是打雜！

programme.title: 野外步出[粵]
programme.desc: 奶仔與嘉賓李旻芳是藝員訓練班的師兄妹，這次選擇划雙人獨木舟更與這出身有關？穿上救生衣準備啟程，但甫登艇已遇驚險。二人出海划到海中小島，並在沙灘上自煮韓式部隊鍋，奶仔還「潛來」龍蝦與墨魚加餸？兩位藝訓班畢業生有不少共同話題，旻芳透露當初上課已定下目標向主持領域發展。旻芳又「投訴」奶仔早前於網上節目未有邀請她任嘉賓！今集後記，旻芳稱讚奶仔拍攝認真，也對其主持表現感到滿意，但評分時卻只得六十分？

programme.title: 就是愛美麗[粵/普]
programme.desc: 好的胭脂會為面色加分，美妝達人高毓喬(Minnie)解說霜、粉、膏、液狀胭脂的特色，冷、暖色系膚色適合的胭脂顏色，以及不同臉型塗抹胭脂的技巧。「愛美麗時尚」參觀台北國際美妝展，展覽涵蓋美妝、美髮、美甲和各式保養，更有知名專家到場作分享，彩妝達人小凱老師就為大家推介木質調胭脂。「愛美麗盲測」測試四款開架發售的日本品牌胭脂，評比它們的易推度、妝感和防水度，讓大家選對產品，打造紅粉緋緋好面色。

programme.title: 就是愛美麗[粵/普]
programme.desc: 感冒時要吃維他命C，但原來平常保養也需要它！保養專家袁觀玲解說維他命C的六大功效，提醒大家使用維他命C保養品及口服維他命C產品的注意事項。「網絡紅什麼」教授DIY防過量進食美肌排毒水及瘦小腹排毒水，讓大家喝水喝出美麗。台北市西區最具指標性的購物區西門町，一直是遊客必去的重點行程，「愛美麗時尚」走訪區內一間天然植萃髮廊，客人可護理頭皮，體驗自然有機的玫瑰精露頭皮護理SPA。

programme.title: 以家人之名#2[粵/普]
programme.desc: 陳婷情緒不好，凌霄有次到海潮家裡吃飯，漸漸也成習慣；陳婷發現凌霄私藏照片，不告而別離開家裡；賀梅託海潮照顧賀子秋，一去沒回頭；李尖尖、凌霄和賀子秋在兩個爸爸照顧下已成為高中生。

programme.title: 2024開運救兵[粵]
programme.desc: 東東(黃建東)在2022年鴻運當頭，近來卻諸事不順，主動求三位師傅打救！九運適合穿鮮色服飾，甚麼顏色最旺東東？穿牛仔褲配襯不當竟會破財或「漏財」？裸泳還用晶石為東東提升運氣！往西南方BBQ有助驅走霉運，更可到長洲、大美督「走一轉」行大運；家居方面，東東的住所有本港樓宇常見的缺角問題，Depp有何建議？慧慧教授「除霉」魔法，燃點迷迭香或薰衣草等草藥，用煙霧為東東清除負能量，房間的霉氣又應如何掃除？

programme.title: 娛樂新聞報道
programme.desc: 每晚緊貼香港娛樂圈的消息，以至世界各地的影視娛樂新聞，報道藝人最新動態、劇集和電影宣傳、演唱會精華、頒獎禮盛況等，甚至遠赴外地採訪娛樂盛事、追蹤各地影星，專訪觀眾熟悉的歌、影、視紅人，讓大家瞬間掌握影視娛樂圈的動態和最新消息。

programme.title: 古靈精怪 台灣篇[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 參拜虎爺有特定儀式，供品亦要投其所好？虎爺附身乩童在地上爬行，也向信眾派「好運雞蛋」。吃蛋前要用蛋敲頭去除霉運，暉哥一擊即中，茜佳、宇夫卻怕痛……見識另一動物神明，台南有廟宇供奉恐龍，神像造型更激似經典怪獸角色，背後有段故！民俗療法五花八門，鋼刀按摩是甚麼玩法？主持們看着刀在身上、頭部敲打，舒服得來不免心慌慌！舊式火車車廂變土地公廟，既成鐵路公司員工上、下班「精神打卡」點，也吸引街坊祈求神明庇佑。

programme.desc: 廣州，粵菜發源地之一，廣府菜的中心，是每一位食客都無法拒絕的美食聖地。愛吃愛玩的主持人麥包，在廣州徹底釋放了吃貨天性，走遍大街小巷，尋找地道美食：悠閑早茶、西關小吃、新潮佳饌，夜市小攤...

programme.title: 古靈精怪 台灣篇[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 參拜虎爺有特定儀式，供品亦要投其所好？虎爺附身乩童在地上爬行，也向信眾派「好運雞蛋」。吃蛋前要用蛋敲頭去除霉運，暉哥一擊即中，茜佳、宇夫卻怕痛……見識另一動物神明，台南有廟宇供奉恐龍，神像造型更激似經典怪獸角色，背後有段故！民俗療法五花八門，鋼刀按摩是甚麼玩法？主持們看着刀在身上、頭部敲打，舒服得來不免心慌慌！舊式火車車廂變土地公廟，既成鐵路公司員工上、下班「精神打卡」點，也吸引街坊祈求神明庇佑。

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#19[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 故事講述一名背叛了丈夫和生病的兒子，為了愛情和慾望拋家棄子的母親，與懷著對母親怨恨的女兒多年後再次見面，並開始對自己母親展開復仇計畫。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 激勵演說家車志健對於待人處事自有一番見解，更曾上載一條「教人不介意做衰人」的短片，其實只是希望大家勇於表達自己的真實思想。志健相信「近朱者赤，近墨者黑」，並提到某些人士不宜結交，當中有何特徵？志健經常鼓勵人要突破、超越自我，而他從健身教練「變身」教導銷售技巧的導師，便是現成例子。志健認為人的潛能無限，只要肯花心思、時間，做任何事皆可成功。Bob就此提出對方做生意失敗的經歷，志健又怎樣回應？

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 見工是一門學問，要如何表現自己才可得到僱主垂青？嘉賓車志健以自我推銷比喻面試，還解釋穿著儀容與資料搜集對面試的重要性。志健提到一個不少見工者的常犯錯誤，就是自我介紹時複述履歷表上的工作經驗，怎樣才是恰當做法？Bob亦趁機分享可令老闆留下深刻印象的面試秘訣！僱主常會要求應徵人士細說自己的長處與短處，應該如何回答方能增加受聘機會？志健又建議求職者在公司與個人同步發展一環多作思考，這樣才可望突圍而出！

programme.title: Politics - Nuclear Blackmail
programme.desc: The Zaporozhye nuclear plant in Energodar is the largest in Europe. programme.title: Politics - Serbia’s Choice
programme.desc: The long-lasting friendship between Russia and Serbia is currently being tested. While Serbia is trying to maintain a relationship with Russia, Western countries are pushing it to impose sanctions on Russia. programme.title: Health - No Fun in the Sun
programme.desc: Camp Sundown is no ordinary summer camp because the fun doesn't start until after dark. These campers live with rare genetic disorders that make exposure to sunlight very painful, or even deadly. Unable to repair skin cells that get damaged by natural light, they have to take numerous precautions and steer clear of all the fun usually associated with sun shine. At Camp Sundown, these extraordinary children can enjoy ordinary activities with peers from around the world who have the same condition.

programme.title: Society - Donbass: That’s Why I’m Here
programme.desc: British Press TV correspondent Johnny Miller came to Ukraine to provide an unbiased account of the conflict in Donbass. However, after he sent a journalistic inquiry, he was immediately placed on a “Myrotvorets” kill list by Ukrainian nationalists. And this is not a rare case. Western media turn a blind eye to the atrocities committed by the Kiev regime. This is why Miller and other foreign journalists are ready to risk their lives and report what they really face in Ukraine.

programme.title: Sport - Esports. Tapping for Glory
programme.desc: Playing video games is no longer just a fun pastime for teenagers. It’s become a high-paying job and a fully-fledged entertainment industry that rivals Hollywood in terms of production and marketing costs. Professional cyber athletes train hard and earn millions of dollars, just like mainstream sportsmen.

programme.title: Here and Now - Here and Now. Andrey Solovyev
programme.desc: The opponent's primary goal is to destroy the Heavy Flamethrower System at all costs, making resistance challenging. Commander Andrey Solovyev discusses the team's most challenging tasks and struggles, especially when the enemy hides behind residential buildings, using women and children as human shields.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - A Worrying Time - Newborn Russia (E39)
programme.desc: It’s the first baby for Natalya, and she is overdue. The doctors are worried and try to induce labour. With husband Aleksandr looking on she eventually gives birth to little Margarita. Having tried IVF treatment, Polina and Vladislav were surprised when she became pregnant naturally. As the baby shows signs of stress, the doctors perform a successful C-section.

programme.title: Human Rights - Marriage Scammer: Till Cash Do Us Part
programme.desc: Alina Milennaya, a resident of Volgograd, Russia, encountered a charismatic man on a dating website. Seduced by promises of a joyful future, she sold her apartment and car in anticipation of their wedding. It was later revealed that he was, in fact, Dmitry Frolov, a notorious marriage scammer with numerous aliases and countless victims. Watch the documentary to discover how Alina handled the tough situation and even assisted the police to arrest the scammer who beguiled her.

programme.title: Arts and Culture - Dangerous Music
programme.desc: For years, music was banned in Afghanistan as sinful, but now one school for children is planting the seeds for traditional Afghan music’s rebirth. Conservative views have left their mark, however, and the school and its young musicians face threats from some elements in society.

programme.title: Military and War - Mariupol: A Homecoming
programme.desc: The Azov nationalist battalion didn’t let civilians out of Mariupol. Instead, they deliberately placed citizens in the buildings where firing points were hidden. Those who resisted were shot. Scare tactics against ordinary people aimed to make them an obedient human shield. Today, when the Battle for Mariupol is over, people are ready to share their pain. So how did Mariupol withstand the Ukrainian nationalist attacks?

programme.title: Politics - Mali: Au Revoir, France
programme.desc: Last year, France withdrew its troops from Mali. This marked the end of a nine-year military operation, aimed at resolving the internal conflict and liberating Mali's territory from Al-Qaeda terrorists. However, according to locals, the French left without providing any tangible assistance, causing further destruction and numerous deaths among the civilian population. ‘Operation Barkhane was launched as part of a French plot to partition Mali’, believes political activist Aboubacar Sidick Fomba. Today, Malians are ready to fight against the dark legacy of colonisation. Will they succeed?

programme.title: Meeting with Nature - It's a Pandaful Life!

Despite IAEA warnings and the referendum, Kiev continues to use the Zaporozhye plant as a blackmail tool. The documentary shows the timeline of the attacks and focuses on potential risks of Ukrainian provocations.

programme.title: Sport - Esports. Tapping for Glory
programme.desc: Playing video games is no longer just a fun pastime for teenagers. It’s become a high-paying job and a fully-fledged entertainment industry that rivals Hollywood in terms of production and marketing costs. Professional cyber athletes train hard and earn millions of dollars, just like mainstream sportsmen.

programme.title: Society - Donbass: That’s Why I’m Here
programme.desc: British Press TV correspondent Johnny Miller came to Ukraine to provide an unbiased account of the conflict in Donbass. However, after he sent a journalistic inquiry, he was immediately placed on a “Myrotvorets” kill list by Ukrainian nationalists. And this is not a rare case. Western media turn a blind eye to the atrocities committed by the Kiev regime. This is why Miller and other foreign journalists are ready to risk their lives and report what they really face in Ukraine.

programme.title: Health - No Fun in the Sun
programme.desc: Camp Sundown is no ordinary summer camp because the fun doesn't start until after dark. These campers live with rare genetic disorders that make exposure to sunlight very painful, or even deadly. Unable to repair skin cells that get damaged by natural light, they have to take numerous precautions and steer clear of all the fun usually associated with sun shine. At Camp Sundown, these extraordinary children can enjoy ordinary activities with peers from around the world who have the same condition.

programme.title: Military and War - Mariupol: A Homecoming
programme.desc: The Azov nationalist battalion didn’t let civilians out of Mariupol. Instead, they deliberately placed citizens in the buildings where firing points were hidden. Those who resisted were shot. Scare tactics against ordinary people aimed to make them an obedient human shield. Today, when the Battle for Mariupol is over, people are ready to share their pain. So how did Mariupol withstand the Ukrainian nationalist attacks?

programme.title: Arts and Culture - Dangerous Music
programme.desc: For years, music was banned in Afghanistan as sinful, but now one school for children is planting the seeds for traditional Afghan music’s rebirth. Conservative views have left their mark, however, and the school and its young musicians face threats from some elements in society.

programme.title: The Silk Road Series - Language of the Silk Road
programme.desc: Modern China is a unique mix of cutting-edge technology and centuries-old tradition. It takes pride in its booming economy and rich cultural heritage. In many ways, China owes its complexity and versatility to the Silk Road, an ancient trade route established in the 2nd century BC that for hundreds of years initiated cross-cultural interaction between Eurasian civilisations.

programme.title: Politics - Mali: Au Revoir, France
programme.desc: Last year, France withdrew its troops from Mali. This marked the end of a nine-year military operation, aimed at resolving the internal conflict and liberating Mali's territory from Al-Qaeda terrorists. However, according to locals, the French left without providing any tangible assistance, causing further destruction and numerous deaths among the civilian population. ‘Operation Barkhane was launched as part of a French plot to partition Mali’, believes political activist Aboubacar Sidick Fomba. Today, Malians are ready to fight against the dark legacy of colonisation. Will they succeed?

programme.title: Newborn Russia - A Worrying Time - Newborn Russia (E39)
programme.desc: It’s the first baby for Natalya, and she is overdue. The doctors are worried and try to induce labour. With husband Aleksandr looking on she eventually gives birth to little Margarita. Having tried IVF treatment, Polina and Vladislav were surprised when she became pregnant naturally. As the baby shows signs of stress, the doctors perform a successful C-section.

programme.title: Human Rights - Marriage Scammer: Till Cash Do Us Part
programme.desc: Alina Milennaya, a resident of Volgograd, Russia, encountered a charismatic man on a dating website. Seduced by promises of a joyful future, she sold her apartment and car in anticipation of their wedding. It was later revealed that he was, in fact, Dmitry Frolov, a notorious marriage scammer with numerous aliases and countless victims. Watch the documentary to discover how Alina handled the tough situation and even assisted the police to arrest the scammer who beguiled her.

programme.title: Military and War - Donbass: The Flipside of War
programme.desc: Every day, volunteers from the NGO 'Memorial: We Shall Not Forget, We Shall Not Forgive' head into the battered cities and towns of the Lugansk People's Republic. Risking their lives, they help locate, identify, and ensure a dignified burial for the victims of Ukrainian shelling in Donbass.

programme.title: Society - Love Commandos
programme.desc: Much like Romeo and Juliet, Indian couples who have married against their parents’ wishes often face violence or even death. This is where the ‘Love Commandos’ come in. This volunteer group helps young people in love stay together and enforce their legal rights despite societal norms.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - A Little Miracle - Newborn Russia (E40)
programme.desc: A medical problem meant Larisa thought she could never have a second child. However, after nine years she underwent successful IVF treatment and is now expecting a boy. The baby is closely monitored, and it’s decided to induce labour. With the calming influence of husband Aleksey in the delivery room, Larisa eventually gives birth to a healthy baby boy.

programme.title: Lifestyle - I am John Kopiski, a Russian Farmer
programme.desc: John Kopiski, a native of the UK, is an unlikely farmer. He's been the proud owner of a dairy farm not far from Moscow for some 20 years. The former business executive with no background in farming decided to pursue a completely new life after visiting Russia back in the ’90s. After converting to Orthodoxy and marrying a Russian, he gradually morphed into an archetypical farmer worthy of a Tolstoy novel.
